fields.description:
In the following [function|https://github.com/apache/hadoop/blob/trunk/hadoop-common-project/hadoop-common/src/main/java/org/apache/hadoop/conf/Configuration.java#L2739]. 

When the attr is in the list of final attrs it just outputs this message without actually updating any resources as per my understanding. 

We change this to debug logging.
fields.summary: Change logging of warning message : "an attempt to override final parameter:"

comments.body: Errr, isn't this the warning that users see to let them know that they can't actually override that value rather than silently fail?
hmm. ryt. We could also change the LOG level to debug level instead of info for this message so that it does not get un-necessarily printed all the time.
sorry for the typo above. Replace the level of the message to debug instead of warn.
